description:
Will Call of Duty: Black Ops 6 move the needle for Xbox Game Pass?
Video Notes: Xbox has confirmed that the next Call of Duty, Black Ops 6, will be coming to its Game Pass subscription service. On this week’s Spot On, Tam and Lucy discuss whether they think BLOPS 6 will be the title to give Game Pass a much needed shot in the arm. 

#gaming #CallOFDuty #gamespot
title: Call of Duty: Game Pass' Savior? | Spot On

In EA SPORTS College Football 25 for PlayStation5 and Xbox Series X|S, experience explosive gameplay variety across 134 FBS schools and immerse yourself in the iconic atmospheres of college football as you chase college greatness.

Introducing the MVP Bundle, including EA SPORTS College Football 25, Madden 25, and bonus rewards to help you make game day every day.
